07:04.210 --> 07:06.360
Look, relationships
go through this.

07:06.560 --> 07:08.910
You know, at some point,
one person just wishes

07:09.110 --> 07:10.950
there was a button
they could push that would

07:11.150 --> 07:13.390
make the other person go
somewhere else for a while.

07:14.260 --> 07:15.290
Cease to exist?

07:15.490 --> 07:18.830
No. That person still exists.

07:19.030 --> 07:20.250
Oh.

07:20.450 --> 07:24.360
[groans] We came
to this amazing hotel!

07:26.900 --> 07:29.180
