07:29.380 --> 07:31.430
I'm not sure what
there is to say anymore.

07:31.630 --> 07:33.490
What? Stop!

07:34.910 --> 07:36.730
How many good years
do you think we have left?

07:36.930 --> 07:39.020
How many? Twenty?

07:39.220 --> 07:40.330
- Maybe?
- Yeah.

07:41.160 --> 07:43.360
I can remember what
I was doing 20 years ago

07:43.560 --> 07:45.030
like it was last Thursday.

07:45.230 --> 07:47.900
Now, if that's what we have left
from last Thursday until now--

07:48.100 --> 07:49.320
Then we have to have fun!

07:49.520 --> 07:51.580
Then the only real
conversation worth having

07:51.780 --> 07:52.950
would be the one that starts,

07:53.150 --> 07:55.000
"Hey, if that's
what we got left,

07:55.200 --> 07:56.970
are we living our best lives?"

08:00.100 --> 08:02.350
