what are we doing here?

08:02.940 --> 08:03.980
[scoffs]

08:04.850 --> 08:06.060
What are we doing here?

08:06.980 --> 08:09.280
- I'm underdressed for this.
- Yeah.

08:10.030 --> 08:12.640
Because... the only thing
I'm sure of

08:12.840 --> 08:15.570
