10:27.210 --> 10:28.190
Why?

10:28.390 --> 10:29.980
Because you seem
respectable to me.

10:30.180 --> 10:31.900
So, I ask,

10:32.100 --> 10:34.170
what's the matter, buddy?

10:35.260 --> 10:37.320
You're heading home to meatloaf.

10:37.520 --> 10:41.590
And you notice one of
our exotic pixies outside,

10:42.260 --> 10:45.210
bathing in the soft,
purple glow of the neon sign.

10:45.410 --> 10:46.770
And you think, "Wait."

10:48.140 --> 10:51.020
"I believe she just looked
at me with interest."

10:51.940 --> 10:54.170
Now, let me bust that up
for you right now.

10:54.370 --> 10:56.820
As soon as you get her
out of that neon glow--

10:58.030 --> 10:59.140
Jesus!

10:59.340 --> 11:00.810
